freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Continued unexplained loss of temperature sensitivity on left side of body and spasmodic pain in numerous locations ranging down right side of body and running down right leg from groin/hip to toes. Skin pain extremely sensitive to touch.
Numbness along my left trunk and leg. Chronic pain throughout my right body.
Numbness down my left leg and foot. Severe pain from my right underarm down through my right thigh and groin. All unexplained.
The last three days I have had a significant pain inside around my right armpit for which I have no explanation.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I lost my sense of smell several years ago but since receiving the vaccination I have my sense of smell back!
